SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1256 as follows:
1. On Page 6, Line 3, by deleting after the word “person”, the word “shall” and inserting the words
“may, at the discretion of the court,”;
2. On Page 6, Line 6, by inserting after the period, the following language:
“If the court does not require use of an ignition interlock device as a condition of bail, the court shall
include written findings on the reasoning for such decision.”; and
3. By amending the title to conform.
